<p><a name="Appearances_at_Large" id="Appearances_at_Large"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Michael_Chabon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: Appearances at Large">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Appearances at Large</span></h3>
<p>Michael Chabon spoke at Lehigh University about his works and moreover his Jewish-American heritage; the pangs of growing up. When asked by an audience member what were his major literary influences, he referenced Garcia Marquez, among others. (Sunday, March 22rd, 2009)</p>
