<li><a href="http://www.sugarbombs.com/kavalier/index.html" class="external text" title="http://www.sugarbombs.com/kavalier/index.html" rel="nofollow">The Amazing Website of Kavalier &amp; Clay</a>, an unofficial but very thorough site recommended by Chabon.</li>
